    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and runs like a dream. It's been well-loved and looked after, so it's ready to hit the road with its next owner right away. If you're looking for something reliable that still looks great, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
