    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving masterpiece. Powered by the S54B32 straight-six engine, it features individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This unit has had the critical rod bearing service and VANOS solenoid overhaul completed, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are track-ready. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. It retains its factory limited-slip differential and is paired with a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the suspension geometry is dialed in with fresh bushings, offering the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance this chassis is renowned for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
