    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a great new home. It\u2019s been well-loved and is in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and still looks fantastic on the road! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to roll. I've taken good care of it, so it's all set for its next adventure. Drop me a message if you're interested or want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
